In case any of ya'll haven't heard this from me before..........I HATE SNOW!!

Nothing like being at work and talking to a co-worker about the CEO of hte company that your company is contracted to work for and having the Co-CEO come down the stairs and ask if the papers are here yet.  Oy!!!

Really now.....is it possible at all for life to suck any worse? Well I'm sure it is, but right now it doesn't feel like it could.  I have a huge fucking heache and a pain in my ass.  Two pains in my ass. Ones really a pain in my ass...I htink I pulled a muscle or something. and the other is a person being a pain in my ass.  I hate it when you actually have to think and shit.  Lets take a poll....do I believe this guy or not?!?!  Who's for me believing him and who's against it?  Personally I want to believe him because it would just make everything go away, but part of me tells me WTF he's never done anything right for you to believe him now. Oh well....who knows. Maybe I should just run away and never come back...then I wouldn't have to decide.

Napoleon Dynamite has got to be the most retarded movie I've seen in a long time.  Everybody said how awesome it was and I never heard anything bad about it.  I don't get why it was good at all.  I mean some parts were funny but nothing was halarious and the entire movie I was waiting for a point and then the movie ended.  Icky poo is my rating of that movie.

New York was fun. There are a hella lotta people there. The worst part about NY is they have awesome looking soft pretzels at the hot dogs vendors on the corner...they were huge and looked really yummy....but they don't freakin' have CHEESE. Whats up with that? You can't have a pretzel without cheese.  And nowhere in NY had cheese...it was crazy.  They all looked at us weird when we asked for cheese too.  Next trip.....San Fran to see Alcatraz!!!
My floor is done. Yippy. I got a new couch thing....and thats about it. My life still sucks....nothing new. Going to New York next weekend, fun times.
Life sucks....oh wait, thats nothing new. I am laying wood flooring in my house.....yeah, thats about all that new.

So I've realized I don't really post in my livejournal that much....and why?!?  Because nothing in my life is worth posting about except my buddy Basco (the dog).  And he really ins't into be written about, just eating and sleeping. Heh.  He gets more love than I do...not that it's a big surprise or anything. In my next life, I want to be be a well loved dog. A well loved anything for that matter. I'm not a huge cat fan, but I'd even be a damn cat if it meant I could be loved. Yeah right....like I even have a chance.
So I downloaded foxfire. I'm not sure if I like it...it's kinda wierd. I don't play arond enough on the internet to like new things!! <font color="#ffff00">Haha. </font>

Well I didn't get my boss' job and I'm fucking pissed off. I worked my ass off for that position and got fucked. They hired somebody before I even had my interview for it. Hello....like I wasn't the best qualified. I would think I would be more qualified than a supervisor from a different site. This Fucking SUCKS!!  This is bullshit. I am getting fucked out of everything. I hate life.

Life is full of shit....nothing else. There is no point to life. Is all just a period of time in out lives that we get to interact with each other rather than just laying around wait to be fertilized or laying around getting eaten away by everything housed in the ground. Thats all what life is about. Getting screwed. Or perhaps I just have a bad prospective on life, but god damn, nothing good ever happens to me....EVER.  I can't think of the last thing that was good that happened to me. I thought it was when Jenny and I stopped fighting, but HA, that was all a wasted effort. I seriously can't remember ANYTHING good happening to me within the past 10 years pretty much. Everything I thought was good at the time....turned out to be bad. LIFE FUCKING SUCKS!! If this isn't hell, I sure don't want to find out what hell is like. I just want to fucking have something good happen....it could start by not getting shit on all the time.

My mom lies to me more than a presidentail campaign and now my best freind seem to have the same problem. Dude...am I really that hard to talk to. Jesus christ, I can't get anybody to just be honest with me all the time. Sometimes I wonder why we have friends and family....why don't we all just get deserted at birth to wild animals so that we don't have to deal with other humans because is all they do is make you feel like shit. I'm so fucking sick of getting shit on, I can't take it anymore. LIFE JUST FUCKING SUCKS!

I read an article today about a guy and his buddies found some money burried behind one of their homes. At the end of the article is says, "I'd rather just burn the money than cause problems with my friends." Sometimes I wish you could do that with people.  As all of you who read this know, Jenny and I are fighting like an old married couple, but whenever I ask anybody for advice I get the same answer. Is fighting over a guy really worth your friendship? Of course I say no, but I'm sure she is getting some of the same advice and if she thinks I am worth losing over a guy, shouldn't I think she is worth losing over a guy?  Though I can't feel that way about somebody I've been best friends with for like 6 years, I wish I could sometimes. I don't think any of my friends are worth losing over a guy, even my friends that I'm not really that close with I wouldn't think are worth losing for a guy. Somebody once told me, "a best friend is somebody you'll always have around," I guess if thats true, I never really had a best friend then. Not that at the time I didn't think that we'd be friends forever, but right now, it seems like we'll never be friends again. Who knows anymore 'cause I sure don't, 'cause right now my life feels like I've spent the last 6 years being friends with somebody so that they could get to the next mountain top, just to throw me over the edge.
I'm alive. Just thought I'd let the people who read this know.....not that anybody really cares.

Nevermind it doesn't matter, it wouldn't be belived even if I said it. I guess everything I say is bullshit....which makes 6 years of friendship bullshit I guess. Nothing like knowing you've wasted 6 years of your life being friends with somebody that didn't believe you.

Question.....

I got in a fight the other day because somebody said something horrible about somebody else and I didn't agree with it. So of course I let them know I didn't agree with it and I ended up in a fight. Like a fist fight. So the question is, do you tell the person it was about, or do you just pretend it never happened since the other person in the fight is pretending it never happened?

So today I attempted many many things.....first off....to take the day off of work so I could visit my bro and nephew...oh yeah, and sister in law.  how'd my day off start.....with a phone call at 12:30am....thats right, midnight thirty on my day off. Anyhow...you can imagine how it went from there, and it ain't getting better from here on out. At leaest I still have xbox live.
And now it's 3:48.......and I'm still awake. I love my job....blah.

It is 1:39AM and once again I am at work. ya know how you can tell if I'm at work or not....'cause I sure as hell wouldn't be up right now if I wasn't at work. I would be getting up in a couple hours to go to work though which is just as bad. I'm so fucking tired.  I've slept 45 minutes because I had something on my mind to talk to Jen about so I coudln't sleep. And then of course, when I go to her house to talk to her, I can't spit it out. I hate that.  I want so much to be able to talk sometimes, but things don't come out. Oh well, someday....
I guess I'm just a wiener and a loser...eh

You Are 70% Left Brained, 30% Right Brained
The left side of your brain controls verbal ability, attention to detail, and reasoning. Left brained people are good at communication and persuading others. If you're left brained, you are likely good at math and logic. Your left brain prefers dogs, reading, and quiet. The right side of your brain is all about creativity and flexibility. Daring and intuitive, right brained people see the world in their unique way. If you're right brained, you likely have a talent for creative writing and art. Your right brain prefers day dreaming, philosophy, and sports.

Take the quiz: "Your Psych-Ward diagnosis"

Accute Stress/Post traumatic Stress disorder
Diagnosis: Post Traumatic Stress Disorder. mental disorder that follows an occurrence of extreme psychological stress, such as that encountered in war or resulting from violence, childhood abuse, sexual abuse, or serious accident. The stressful event is usually followed by a period of emotional numbness and denial that can last for months or years. After that period, symptoms such as recurring nightmares, flashbacks, short-term memory problems, insomnia, or heightened sensitivity to sudden noises may begin. In some cases outbursts of violent behavior have been observed.
